  "title": "Garlicky Gooey Norwegian Soya Milk Stir-fry",
  "description": "This adventurous dish combines the savory notes of garlic with a gooey texture from soya milk in a gluten-free-friendly meal that's perfect for breakfast, lunch, or dinner.",
